name: Terrell's Transit Directions
tagline: Transit directions for travel via public transportation in New York City.
body:
### Welcome to Terrell's Transit Directions!   
I will be using this site to display my transportation 'documents' for use in travelling through New York City. Hopefully this will be easier for me to edit than Google Docs, so let's see!  
-- Terrell Merritt
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
